,{"pid":"bf2a6bcd384077dd834267297a49d78e3a64971e","tid":904990,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:02:20.000Z","msg":"泡沫經濟概起點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爆就一齊死<br />\n所以口講支爆<br />\n一爆就都係窮人死先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc015148cef87bcdc91a67f92e8851a39ca0b1c0","tid":904990,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fb855635fe87f1ce58eaafbdf61681fc91ced7f","tid":904990,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"706f12c24c6998eab70e22051c9db652081d5b56","tid":904990,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a93ed52bc63f6d52f00111ded4f5d40f6adbbed","tid":904990,"uid":59047,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為保障存款者的利益，基本上所有接收存款的銀行都需按照相關的法定要求，只能借出部分的存款，並留有一定比例的存款準備金。若法定的存款準備金比率為10％，而銀行的存款為＄10,000，相應的存款準備金便為＄1,000。 假設某銀行的資產負債表如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8jry3L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8jry3L.png&h=9bb04dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在以上例子中，銀行的存款準備金為＄1,000，達到了法定要求的水平（＄1,000／＄10,000＝10％）。此外，銀行亦額外保留了＄1,000的超額準備金，並借出了＄9,000 。<br />\n<br />\n若出現了銀行擠提，大量的客戶從銀行中提款，總提款額達＄2,000，銀行的存款便會由＄10,000減少＄2,000至＄8,000。這＄2,000亦會即時由銀行的準備金支付。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X6Ery3Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX6Ery3Q.png&h=110fd150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於存款減少至＄8,000，相應的法定存款準備金便由＄1,000（＄10,000＊10％）下降至＄800（＄8,000＊10％），但銀行的準備金已全數用於應付＄2,000的提款。因此，銀行便需籌集資金以應付其準備金的不足。通常地說，銀行可透過以下兩個渠道來解決以上情況：<br />\n<br />\n（一）向中央銀行或其他金融機構借貸＄800：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cmhdd3T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCmhdd3T.png&h=8cab8ea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（二）減少貸款＄800：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXgtNoY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXgtNoY.png&h=fa125678&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁點解銀行唔用全部存款＄10,000做準備金，然後借＄100,000出去？<br />\n都係10%，符合法定要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"你右邊得$10,000+$1,000，點借$100,000出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔通又問人借<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:37:32.000Z","msg":"money multiplication <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假設d 人借完錢做完生意最後d 錢返入銀行系統"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:20:19.000Z","msg":"哩個又係另一個概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58120bee89bc49d1cc274ed744d8faa0f61fd047","tid":904990,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf2a6bcd384077dd834267297a49d78e3a64971e","tid":904990,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:02:20.000Z","msg":"泡沫經濟概起點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爆就一齊死<br />\n所以口講支爆<br />\n一爆就都係窮人死先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 何解<br />\n其實任何嘢爆都係窮人死先"}]}